---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="The New Priesthood — Sun Worship — Nazaryah"
  description="Every religion has a class of men who interpret the unseen for the masses. The ancient world had the priests of Ra. The modern world has NASA."
>
  <div class="sw-wrap">

    <!-- ── HERO ── -->
    <section class="sw-hero">
      <p class="sw-label">&#8213; Sun Worship &#8213;</p>
      <h1 class="sw-title">The New Priesthood</h1>
      <p class="sw-sub">
        Lab coats replaced robes. Composite images replaced idols. The congregation moved from the temple to the classroom — but the function is identical.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- ── INTRO ── -->
    <section class="sw-section">
      <div class="sw-prose">
        <p>
          Every religion has a class of men who interpret the unseen for the masses — men who are not to be questioned, whose images and declarations are accepted on faith alone. The ancient world had the priests of Ra and Baal. The modern world has NASA.
        </p>
        <p>
          Lab coats replaced robes, composite images replaced idols, and the congregation moved from the temple to the classroom — but the function is identical. The people are told what the universe looks like by a small group of men they will never meet, using instruments they will never see, producing images they did not take.
        </p>
        <p>
          This page examines how the space establishment operates as a religious institution, demanding faith in what no common man has ever independently verified.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── COMING SOON ── -->
    <section class="sw-section sw-section-alt">
      <div class="sw-prose sw-coming-soon">
        <div class="sw-soon-icon">&#9685;</div>
        <h2 class="sw-soon-title">Full Study Coming</h2>
        <p>
          This study is being assembled — covering the occult founders of JPL and NASA, the role of Jack Parsons and Aleister Crowley, the nature of composite imagery presented as photography, and the religious architecture built around the space program.
        </p>
        <p>
          Return to the <a href="/sun-worship" class="sw-link">Sun Worship hub</a> or read <a href="/sun-worship/the-ancient-lie" class="sw-link">The Ancient Lie</a> for the full historical thread while this page is being built.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── QUOTE ── -->
    <section class="sw-footer-quote">
      <p class="sw-quote-text">"Professing themselves to be wise, they became fools, and changed the glory of the incorruptible Elohim into an image made like to corruptible man."</p>
      <p class="sw-quote-ref">— Romans 1:22–23</p>
    </section>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .sw-wrap {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0e0904 0%, #1a1208 20%, #160f07 100%);
    color: #f0e0bf;
    font-family: 'Crimson Pro', 'Crimson Text', Georgia, serif;
    min-height: 80vh;
  }

  .sw-hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem 3.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #4a3218;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 0%, rgba(180, 100, 20, 0.2), transparent 70%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, #0a0602 0%, #1a1208 100%);
  }

  .sw-label {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    color: #8a6028;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .sw-title {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #f0e0bf;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .sw-sub {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.2rem);
    color: #c4a46b;
    font-style: italic;
    max-width: 580px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .sw-section {
    padding: 3.5rem 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #2e1f0d;
  }

  .sw-section-alt {
    background: rgba(10, 6, 2, 0.3);
  }

  .sw-prose {
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.85;
    color: #d9c9a8;
  }

  .sw-prose p { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .sw-prose p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

  .sw-link {
    color: #BA7517;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }
  .sw-link:hover { color: #d4930f; }

  .sw-coming-soon {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .sw-soon-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: #5a3a10;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .sw-soon-title {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #c4a46b;
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
  }

  .sw-footer-quote {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #160f07 0%, #0e0904 100%);
  }

  .sw-quote-text {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.2rem);
    font-style: italic;
    color: #c4a46b;
    max-width: 620px;
    margin: 0 auto 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .sw-quote-ref {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    color: #5a3e1a;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
</style>
